## table card | under=tpl_project | doc="Archive screen (NEW in Gate 11). Terminal-phase rows. The 'Last 30 days' time-window filter card lands in a future gate when closed_at exists as a real attribute; for now the phase_scope toggle alone selects the row set." | on_conflict="id"
### rows
